<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.4.5">
<l>appaṅ kalantaciṟ ṟuṇṭi yakkāram pāliṟ kalanta</l>
<l>coppaṭa nāṉcuṭṭu vaittēṉ tiṉṉa luṟutiyēl nampi</l>
<l>ceppiḷa meṉmulai yārkaḷ ciṟupuṟam pēcic cirippar</l>
<l>coppaṭa nīrāṭa vēṇṭuñ cōttam pirāṉiṅkē vārāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Nampi! If you are desirous of eating,</l>
<l>I [have made] sweet pastry balls mixed with ricecakes</l>
<l>and sugar mixed in milk [and] kept [them] good and hot.</l>
<l>Praiseworthy Lord! [You] need a thorough bathing in water,</l>
<l>those [girls] with soft, young, copper-pot [like] breasts</l>
<l>will laugh and spread petty gossip [about you]. Come here!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
